headline: Jefferies Increased the Price Objective of Paycom Software, Inc. (PAYC)
summary: Jefferies has maintained its Hold rating on Paycom Software, Inc. (NYSE:PAYC) but increased its price target from $130 to $155. This modification reflects an updated assessment of Paycom Software, Inc.
